    option2: ...the story of Rama.
    option3: ...the story of the Pandavas and the Khauravas
    option4: ...an ancient collection of animal fables.
    option1IsCorrect: 0
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 0
    option4IsCorrect: 1
